OL,3,CMan, 52, dies after eating broccoli
OL,4,Csandwich in southern Italy
OL,6,FAuthorities in southern Italy are
OL,7,Fresponding to a toxic botulism
OL,8,Foutbreak after one man died and nine
OL,9,Fothers were hospitalised after eating
OL,10,Fbroccoli sandwiches.
OL,12,FArtist Luigi Di Sarno, 52, collapsed
OL,13,Fafter eating the sandwich, which was
OL,14,Fallegedly contaminated, from a food
OL,15,Ftruck in the Cosenza province.
OL,17,FNine others were taken to the
OL,18,Fintensive care unit of Annunziata
OL,19,FHospital, including two teenagers and
OL,20,Ftwo women in their 40s.
