OL,3,CMan, 52, dies after eating broccoli
OL,4,Csandwich in southern Italy
OL,6,FBotulism is a rare but life-
OL,7,Fthreatening condition caused by toxins
OL,8,Fproduced by Clostridium botulinum
OL,9,Fbacteria.
OL,11,FThese toxins attack the nervous system
OL,12,Fand can cause paralysis but can be
OL,13,Ftreated.
OL,15,FFollowing the outbreak in the Cosenza
OL,16,Fregion, officials have ordered the
OL,17,Fimmediate seizure of a commercial
OL,18,Fproduct, which is thought to be
OL,19,Fbroccoli in oil.
