OL,6,FThe food truck which sold the
OL,7,Fsandwiches has also been seized, while
OL,8,Fan anti-toxin serum used to treat
OL,9,Fbotulism is being distributed across
OL,10,FItaly.
OL,12,FMaria Rosaria Campitiello, Head of the
OL,13,FDepartment of Prevention, Research,
OL,14,Fand Health Emergencies said patients
OL,15,Fwere provided with access to
OL,16,F"lifesaving antidote treatments".
