OL,6,F"It should be noted that the foods at
OL,7,Frisk of botulinum toxin are homemade
OL,8,Fpreserves prepared vacuum-packed, in
OL,9,Foil, or in water, and, rarely,
OL,10,Findustrial products," she said.
OL,12,F"This is why it is important to follow
OL,13,Fthe rules for the correct and safe
OL,14,Fpreparation and storage of food."
