OL,6,FThe Poison Control Centre in Pavia is
OL,7,Fthe designated hub to manage the
OL,8,Fbotulism outbreak, including
OL,9,Fdiagnosing the cases.
OL,11,FLaw enforcement agencies, medical
OL,12,Fservices and the Red Cross are working
OL,13,Ftogether to provide treatment.
OL,15,FMr Di Sarno's family spoke to local
OL,16,Fmedia, calling for justice.
OL,18,FHis sister Mena Di Sarno told
OL,19,FInterNapoli the 52-year-old was
OL,20,Fdischarged from hospital despite still
OL,21,Ffeeling unwell and dizzy.
